# sira router dhcp reservation evidence — 20260426

status: reservation-evidence-recorded
created_at: 2026-04-26 14:50:46
repo_root: /Users/thien/Desktop/Hồ Sơ SHTT/ natt-os_verANC

---

## 1. purpose

đóng bằng chứng ip tĩnh cho imac physical server.

ưu tiên router dhcp reservation theo mac address của cổng ethernet.

không khai ipv6 sống trong bước này.

---

## 2. wired edge

- device: en0
- wired_edge_ip: 192.168.1.199
- mac_address: 50:1f:c6:5b:b0:f5
- router_gateway: 192.168.1.1
- primary_edge: wired_edge
- wifi_edge: secondary
- ipv6: deferred

---

## 3. router action required

trên router, đặt dhcp reservation:

```text
mac_address = 50:1f:c6:5b:b0:f5
reserved_ip = 192.168.1.199
name = imac-natt-os-wired-edge
```

---

